PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of MERVYN C. RUSSELL, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of seven months, effective July 1, 1998.
